title: Power is YOUR Obligation, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO226
itunes:title: Power is YOUR Obligation, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO226
description: Do you consider yourself a good person? Do you seek power? If you answered “yes” to both questions, great. If you answered “yes” to the first but “no” to the second, what the f*ck is wrong with you? You’re what’s wrong with society. You’re the reason the world isn’t a better place. What do I mean? Listen to this episode and find out.
